SECURITY NOTICE:

This software includes End-to-End Encryption (E2EE) capabilities. Users are 
responsible for compliance with local encryption laws and export regulations. 
The encryption implementation is provided for legitimate security purposes and 
educational use.

DISCLAIMER:

While this implementation uses military-grade encryption algorithms, no system 
is 100% secure. Users should:
- Regularly update cryptographic libraries
- Follow proper operational security practices
- Conduct regular security audits
- Implement proper key management procedures

The authors and contributors are not responsible for any security breaches, 
data loss, or misuse of the encryption capabilities provided by this software.
